{"tid":1904861,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「求助」遇到uber騙徒司機！！！","createTime":"2020-02-29T23:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T06:17:36.000Z","uid":169028,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5abe95287763c8e6b5f5aeaace320adb432f85","tid":1904861,"uid":169028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T23:21:36.000Z","msg":"啱啱清晨6點幾個陣 <br />\n係朋友屋企走 就call咗架uber<br />\n個司機好快接左單<br />\n然後收到個訊息係code number<br />\n個司機係app到chat我拎code<br />\n我比左佢之後就已讀不回 打電話都唔聽<br />\n架車仲要無黎過！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nuber app一直hold住係同一個版面<br />\n咩都做唔到 如果cancel左張單又會收我錢<br />\n因為過咗5分鐘... ...<br />\n依家唔知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人試過遇到咁既情況？<br />\n<br />\n另外，因為架車無黎到<br />\n所以我朋友就用佢電話call<br />\n另一個司機就黎咗接我地<br />\n我地講咗啱先遇到既情況佢聽<br />\n佢話佢都聽過一次有客講過又係咁<br />\n但都係近呢一、兩星期先聽過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉  買口罩已經比人呃咗錢<br />\n依家連call個車都比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd229b6ed5889716bee1c057802d4286d5e72c7","tid":1904861,"uid":63311,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T23:25:35.000Z","msg":"App report 司機玩野"},{"pid":"984813a599a89c65330c9423bc6f9e1ba4927915","tid":1904861,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:15:48.000Z","msg":"拎電話認證嘅code可大可小<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c583af16302a3a28603054abdc1aed2587bfef08","tid":1904861,"uid":169028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd229b6ed5889716bee1c057802d4286d5e72c7","tid":1904861,"uid":63311,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T23:25:35.000Z","msg":"App report 司機玩野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:33:56.000Z","msg":"app裡面個求助到<br />\n無一個選擇係個司機無黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家嘗試Uber facebook到inbox問下"},{"pid":"c5611b38cd879cd4552d8b6816e4165d74201ef4","tid":1904861,"uid":169028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"984813a599a89c65330c9423bc6f9e1ba4927915","tid":1904861,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:15:48.000Z","msg":"拎電話認證嘅code可大可小<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:36:21.000Z","msg":"係香港搭左Uber都2、3年<br />\n都係第一次收到咩行程代碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a39aa590bddb5b1e78db6464711757086e77c61","tid":1904861,"uid":248021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"Code 係咩意思<br />\n<br />\n投訴無乜用 之前試過投訴<br />\n話會聯絡我<br />\n收到一個miss call 未覆返個call就收到email話多謝我同佢講返件事 會跟進<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明無聽到電話"},{"pid":"66e6c0c89431ac8699acab752c4c8730c972269f","tid":1904861,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c583af16302a3a28603054abdc1aed2587bfef08","tid":1904861,"uid":169028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd229b6ed5889716bee1c057802d4286d5e72c7","tid":1904861,"uid":63311,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T23:25:35.000Z","msg":"App report 司機玩野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:33:56.000Z","msg":"app裡面個求助到<br />\n無一個選擇係個司機無黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家嘗試Uber facebook到inbox問下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"鳩揀個原因 跟住再打字 <br />\n之後cs應該會再問"},{"pid":"305f8338313d9bf5078941da6f8445c1a081208f","tid":1904861,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"我未試過拎code<br />\n但我都試過司機賴皮 一開始話上手客漏左野等緊佢返黎拎<br />\n過左唔知幾耐（即係你cancel就扣你錢既時間開始）<br />\n佢